com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube

Class CountDistinctCubeAggregator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube.DefaultCubeAggregator
      • com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube.CountDistinctCubeAggregator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CubeAggregator, DupleCubeAggregator

    public class CountDistinctCubeAggregator
extends DefaultCubeAggregator
implements DupleCubeAggregator
    A memory-efficient implementation of [SUM, COUNT_TO_ONE] DupleCubeAggregator, for the special case when the aggregated column is known to be never null. For example, when the aggregated column is also the inner dimension.
